net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component

Enum Field.InputMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Field.InputMode>
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.Field.InputMode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Field.InputMode>
    Enclosing class:
    Field

    public static enum Field.InputMode
extends Enum<Field.InputMode>
    Input mode. This defines a hint to the browser on which keyboard to display. This applies when the value of the InputType is text, password, email, or url.
